Welcome to iOS Development: Part 1

This course is set up to show you the entrance in the walled garden and give you a tour. You will learn Apple developer tools like Xcode, the Cocoa API framework, and the Objective-C language. At the end of this course, you will have built many simple applications that will expose you to different capabilities of this growing platform.

Check out this Asdf page.

I'm excited to lead you on this tour!

Having more words in the syllabus will help me test a new feature.
